  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare the antitumor efficacy and toxicity of Idarubicin and cytarabine in combination
      with or not with infusions of granulocyte colony-stimulating factor-mobilized HLA-mismatched
      donor peripheral blood stem cells in patients with newly diagnosed high-risk acute myeloid
      leukemia (AML).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
